reviews.review_text:
Some Fall 7:40 into Terrapin Station
  If memory serves me well...that's when the dude flies from upper deck During some rise some fall, Saw him in Vt. some 10 years later at a party house and he was still having surgery's and sporting crutch's. Amazing he was still with us.
 Furthur played 11/15/2011 at The now T.U.C.  in Albany some nearly 21 years later and laid down version of Watchtower into Stella Blue and then they played Last Time... Dozin AT The Knick Hat Trick... 
 Thanks forr the memories
